{"tid":494570,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"喺工廈番工／出入嘅巴絲入一入黎","createTime":"2017-12-09T17:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T09:16:49.000Z","uid":146274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"faee8d811761e0974ccc867c153674df2dd77254","tid":494570,"uid":146274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟係一個滿懷理想同熱誠嘅有為青年，矢志為香港工廈發展出一分微力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家幫緊大學做緊個有關工廈嘅research<br />\n各位出入工廈嘅巴打／絲打，可以的話幫幫手填份問卷，支持下。<br />\n你地嘅支持好緊要，因為如果份論文做得好嘅話，有機會可以俾政府個邊睇，希望可以幫助完善香港嘅工廈政策。<br />\n希望大家可以多多支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/LPAYZ9DVoviAEbDm1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FLPAYZ9DVoviAEbDm1&d=BjJ2hMaJX7GUioK5eM7DqQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=cec68c6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/LPAYZ9DVoviAEbDm1</a><br />\n<br />\n拿哈比人我講多出做得到，J圖喺下面　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/154526_377bf56d01e6b223160103fff94382bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F154526_377bf56d01e6b223160103fff94382bb.jpg&h=d523d632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/154527_38cc6467dea98ad3bb73534a963ad7de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F154527_38cc6467dea98ad3bb73534a963ad7de.jpg&h=ed6dec90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/154528_3c8f9c3b5c3824c828f70ea86ad13453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F154528_3c8f9c3b5c3824c828f70ea86ad13453.jpg&h=71c4f2db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/20